    <title>
        <en>Snapping Productions Pack</en>
    </title>
    <description>
        <en><![CDATA[This mod pack for Farming Simulator 22 features the base game production buildings but set to snap at 45 degree angle rotations only. 
        
        Now you can finally achieve perfectly straight building placement on your farm!
        
        Included in this pack are ALL base game productions: 

            - Factories:
                - Bakery
                - Carpentry
                - Cereal Factory
                - Dairy
                - Grain Mill
                - Oil Mill
                - Grape Processing Unit
                - Spinnery
                - Tailor Shop
                - BioGas Plants (99kw, 250kw and 500kw)
            
            - Selling Points:
                - BioMass Heating Plant
                - Debris Crusher
                - Farmers Market
                - Restaurant
                - Fast Food Restaurant
                - Pizzeria 
                - Supermarket

            - Greenhouses:
                - Large Greenhouse
                - Medium Greenhouse
                - Small Greenhouse

        ]]></en>
    </description>
